6666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/a59e9/fontChange2.webp 192w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/0ca9f/fontChange2.webp 384w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/dc9b9/fontChange2.webp 768w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/e2c2f/fontChange2.webp 1152w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/f3efb/fontChange2.webp 1536w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/373d8/fontChange2.webp 2864w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/3b721/fontChange2.png 192w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/66595/fontChange2.png 384w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/fe486/fontChange2.png 768w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/d2d74/fontChange2.png 1152w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/e8464/fontChange2.png 1536w,\n/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/b1b5c/fontChange2.png 2864w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/80b3b4c80bd5f35cedbfdb42801404a5/fe486/fontChange2.png\"\n            alt=\"fontChange2\"\n            title=\"fontChange2\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n환경의 차이가 있긴 하겠지만 약 1초의 시간이 차이가 나는 상황\n흐으으음 🤔</p>\n<p>단순히 글꼴을 자주 바꾸지않으면 설치하는게 당연히 좋은 상황, 실제로 폰트를 설치해서 쓸지는 추후 고민해보고 적용방법을 소개하려 한다.</p>\n<h2>How?</h2>\n<p>아래 내용은 gatsby 공식사이트에 근거해 작성 했습니다. (2022. 07. 24. 기준)\n<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.com/docs/how-to/styling/using-web-fonts/#self-host-google-fonts-with-fontsource:~:text=Loader%20with%20Typekit-,Self%2Dhost%20Google%20Fonts%20with%20Fontsource,-Other%20resources\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">gatsby 안내 링크 “Fontsource”</a></p>\n<hr>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> @fontsource/open-sans</code></pre></div>\n<p>우선 사용하려는 폰트의 npm 패키지 설치를 설치하고\nGlobalStyle.tsx (인프런 <em>“React 기반 Gastsby로 기술블로그 개발하기”</em> 강의를 통해 만든 블로그 구조 기준)의 폰트를 아래와 같이 바꿔주자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ts\"><pre class=\"language-ts\"><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token string\">'@fontsource/open-sans'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> \n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> defaultStyle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> css<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n    * {\n        padding: 0;\n        margin: 0;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\n        font-family: 'Open Sans', serif;\n    }\n...\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/choice/post/bc70035f-261a-4148-a24d-e5285d5d2435/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h2>To be continue..</h2>\n<p>md 문서 theme를 바꿔 좀더 내가 보기좋은 느낌으로 만들어보려 한다!</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Font Change","summary":"인프런 _\"React 기반 Gastsby로 기술블로그 개발하기\"_ 로 만든 블로그 Customizing하기!","date":"2020.07.24.","categories":["Web","React","Gatsby","WebFont"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/e84a6dc8bf348ae11b107b1e95d7d611/4453e/FontChange.jpg","srcSet":"/static/e84a6dc8bf348ae11b107b1e95d7d611/ae85b/FontChange.jpg 160w,\n/static/e84a6dc8bf348ae11b107b1e95d7d611/c2359/FontChange.jpg 320w,\n/static/e84a6dc8bf348ae11b107b1e95d7d611/4453e/FontChange.jpg 640w","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/e84a6dc8bf348ae11b107b1e95d7d611/e7070/FontChange.webp 160w,\n/static/e84a6dc8bf348ae11b107b1e95d7d611/84334/FontChange.webp 320w,\n/static/e84a6dc8bf348ae11b107b1e95d7d611/7f499/FontChange.webp 640w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 640px) 640px, 100vw"}]},"width":640,"height":398}},"publicURL":"/static/e84a6dc8bf348ae11b107b1e95d7d611/FontChange.jpeg"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/FontChange/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}